<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.3.7">
<l>paṉṟiyu māmaiyum mīṉamu mākiya pāṟkaṭal vaṇṇā vuṉmēl</l>
<l>kaṉṟi ṉuruvāki mēypulat tēvanta kaḷḷa vacuraṉ taṉṉai</l>
<l>ceṉṟu piṭittuc ciṟukkaika ḷālē viḷaṅkā yeṟintāy pōlum</l>
<l>eṉṟumeṉ piḷḷaikkut tīmaikaḷ ceyvārka ḷaṅṅaṉa māvār kaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with the complexion of the milk ocean</l>
<l rend="indent">who became the boar, the tortoise, and the fish!</l>
<l>With [your] little hands, approaching and seizing</l>
<l rend="indent">that demon who came in the field to graze</l>
<l rend="indent">in the form of a calf [to] deceive you,</l>
<l>[now] it seems you have thrown an unripe fruit of the wood-apple tree,</l>
<l rend="indent">those who harass my child always end up like that!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
